help.help:
Shows help documentation for a command, a list of commands with descriptions, or a list of commands within a category.
Examples:
[p]help
[p]help profile
[p]help profile 3ds
[p]help Profile

support.value: For more help, Join the Argonaut Industries Support Server: https://discord.gg/q2j8HtB

help.bot_help:
An explanation of command signatures:
**<argument>**
This means the argument is required.
**[argument]**This means the argument is optional.
**[A|B]**
This means that it can be either A or B.
**[argument...]**
This means you can have multiple, or 0, arguments.
__You do not type in the brackets__

menu.page_msg: There are {} help pages. Send a number to see the corresponding page. Send any other message to exit.
menu.footer: Type {0}help <command> for more info on a command. You can also type {0}help <category> for more info on a category.

buttons.number: Jump to a page by number
buttons.bot_help: Shows general information on how to use the bot

formatting.help_missing: This command does not have any help information.
